tools: sys.write, sys.read, sys.download, sys.find
tools: github.com/gptscript-ai/browser
args: url: Articles link
args: dir: directory to save the created files

1. Browse to the ${url} and read the pages contents
2. Create a tldr text version of it for an instagram reel or youtube short. No emojis and no more than 100 words.
3. split the created text into 3 parts. save the texts to "${dir}/story-${INDEX}.txt"
